text: Qaranwal tanim kee Baaxô Bagul taniimih Reeda inkih Yalli-le, Nummah siinik duma kitab kah yontocowwime maraa kee sin (Mucammad åzsaieýķo ummat kinnuk) inkih Yallak meesita iyyaanamah sin farrimne, Yalli sin edde farriimeemil koroositteenik, toysa diggah Yalli Qaranwal tanim kee Baaxô Bagul taniimih Reeda usuk-le, Yalli isi ginok gaddali isi Naqoosah yecee Niqmatal fayla-li kinni
